{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"nonisolated","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"hidden","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","text":"View","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP"},{"text":"\n","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"return-value","text":"Return Value","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A hidden view.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Hidden views are invisible and can’t receive or respond to interactions.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However, they do remain in the view hierarchy and affect layout. Use","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this modifier if you want to include a view for layout purposes, but","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"don’t want it to display.","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["HStack {","    Image(systemName: \"a.circle.fill\")","    Image(systemName: \"b.circle.fill\")","    Image(systemName: \"c.circle.fill\")","        .hidden()","    Image(systemName: \"d.circle.fill\")","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The third circle takes up space, because it’s still present, but","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"OpenSwiftUI doesn’t draw it onscreen.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you want to conditionally include a view in the view hierarchy, use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"if"},{"type":"text","text":" statement instead:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["VStack {","    HStack {","        Image(systemName: \"a.circle.fill\")","        Image(systemName: \"b.circle.fill\")","        if !isHidden {","            Image(systemName: \"c.circle.fill\")","        }","        Image(systemName: \"d.circle.fill\")","    }","    Toggle(\"Hide\", isOn: $isHidden)","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Depending on the current value of the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isHidden"},{"type":"text","text":" state variable in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"example above, controlled by the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Toggle","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" instance, OpenSwiftUI draws"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the circle or completely omits it from the layout."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/RoundedRectangle\/hidden()","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Hides this view unconditionally.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/roundedrectangle\/hidden()"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","title":"hidden()","role":"symbol","platforms":[{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"name":"iOS","introducedAt":"13.0"},{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"name":"macOS","introducedAt":"10.15"},{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"name":"tvOS","introducedAt":"13.0"},{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"name":"visionOS","introducedAt":"1.0"},{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"name":"watchOS","introducedAt":"6.0"}],"modules":[{"relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"],"name":"OpenSwiftUI"}],"externalID":"s:1